    "Similarly, Gaudio et al. [106] proposed a maximum likelihood-based estimation algorithm for OTFS-ISAC, deriving the CRB bounds for both range and velocity estimation.",
    "Taking advantage of the sparsity of the sensing channel in the Doppler-delay domain, Liu et al. [169] proposed a Bayesian learning-based estimation method for the OTFS-enabled radar system.",
    "Dehkordi et al. [170] proposed a maximum likelihood-based joint target detection and parameter estimation scheme for the OTFS-enabled ISAC system.",
